game.name: Princess Sauna Room
game.description:
Everyone wants to relax after a hectic work schedule - be it at home or in office. Today the beautiful princess Rapunzel along with Ariel and Anna has made out a plan to go to a nearby spa center. Luckily, you work in that spa therapy center. Is not pretty exciting to give these beautiful princesses a wonderful spa as per their choice? Join Princess Sauna Room game and be prepared to play the role of a spa specialist!

Your objective in this brand new makeover game is to help Rapunzel prepare for her most awaited sauna spa therapy. Start the process by giving her a wonderful and refreshing shower. Make sure to take off her jewelry and then work on changing into a more suitable outfit. Other two princesses are already waiting for the rest two in the sauna room. Try to follow the instructions properly to help Rapunzel relax in the optimum possible manner! After a long busy week, these princesses have decided to have a break from their work during the weekend. 

Your responsibility is to help all of them to change their clothes and prepare the sauna room for them. Everything looks to be arranged in a proper way. Follow all the steps as instructed on the screen to complete your task as fast as you can in this html5 princess spa game!
